# ============================================================
# ONE-CELL, SELF-CONTAINED N=1 EXPERIMENT PIPELINE
# ============================================================
# Purpose:
#   1. Verify no-trade wedge:
#        1 - alpha <= R := lambda_y / lambda_x <= 1
#      under alpha, T, eps, t sweeps.
#
#   2. Compare Stage1 and PGDPO/PMP against a 1D numerical benchmark:
#      - regularized trading-rate DP benchmark
#      - same eps is used in:
#           (i) environment dynamics
#          (ii) PMP projection
#         (iii) DP benchmark transition
#
# Important convention:
#   Buy:
#       X decreases by L u^+ dt
#   Sell:
#       X increases by (1-alpha)L u^- dt
#   Quadratic execution:
#       X decreases by 0.5 eps L u^2 dt
#
# Therefore the regularized Hamiltonian projection is:
#
#   u* = [(lambda_y - lambda_x)/(eps lambda_x)]_+
#        - [((1-alpha)lambda_x - lambda_y)/(eps lambda_x)]_+
#
# and the no-trade wedge is unchanged:
#
#   1 - alpha <= lambda_y / lambda_x <= 1.
#
# ============================================================

